meta.description: A Library for doing Number Theory

license.fullName: GNU General Public License v2.0 or later

meta.long_description:
NTL is a high-performance, portable C++ library providing data
structures and algorithms for manipulating signed, arbitrary
length integers, and for vectors, matrices, and polynomials over
the integers and over finite fields.
meta.name: ntl
